    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomy of the carinaless group of Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) (Hymenoptera, Halictidae) from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan, with description of seven new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276449>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276450>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276444> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276449>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) urumaense Murao, sp. nov. A – F: holotype, female. M – O: paratype, female. G – L, P, Q: male, paratype. A, G: lateral habitus. B, H: lower face. C, I: mesoscutum. D, J: sculpture on mesoscutum. E, K: mesoscutellum. F, L: mesepisternum. M, P: labrum. N, Q: propodeal dorsum. O: inner hind tibial spur. Scale bars: N, 0.5 mm; M, P, Q, 0.25 mm; O, 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276449/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276450>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) urumaense Murao, sp. nov. A, C: holotype, female. B, D, E – H: paratype, male. A, B: head in frontal view. C, D: first metasomal tergum (left half, sculpture; right half, hair pattern). E – G: male genitalia (E: left, ventral view; right, dorsal view. F: lateral view. G: retrorse lobe). H: seventh and eighth metasomal sterna. Scale bars: A – D, 1 mm; E, F, H, 0.2 mm; G, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276450/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276444>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Lasioglossum (Evylaeus) canaliculatum Murao, sp. nov. A, C: holotype, female. B, D, E – H: paratype, male. A: head in frontal view. B: metasomal sterna. C, D: first metasomal tergum (left half, sculpture; right half, hair pattern). E – G: male genitalia (E: left, ventral view; right, dorsal view. F: lateral view. G: retrorse lobe). H: seventh and eighth metasomal sterna. Scale bars: A, B, C, D, 1 mm; E, F, H, 0.2 mm; G, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276444/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

